Wave making gospel/juju musician, Prince Abel Dosunmu aka Mega 99, is set to embark on a US tour.  Sponsored by prominent promoter and CEO of Sammek Moments Arts and Cultural Entertainment, the tour, which is the second of its kind, will see the award-winning artiste perform in 22 states in the US. It will take him and his band to New York, New Jersey, Washington DC and Maryland among others. Apart from US, Mega 99 has also taken his creative style of juju music to London, Dubai and some other places abroad. He has remained a force to reckon with in his field. His unique voice and stage craftsmanship are some of the qualities that have endeared him to many over the years. This also explains why he’s always a popular demand among his fans, both home and abroad.